### Get all genres
GET http://localhost:8080/api/genres

### Get a genre by ID (Success)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/genres/1

### Get a genre by ID (Failure - genre not found)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/genres/999

### Add a new genre (Success)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/genres
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Action"
}

### Add a new genre (Failure - missing name)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/genres
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### Delete a genre (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/genres/1

### Delete a genre (Failure - genre not found)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/genres/999

### Get all genres for a movie
GET http://localhost:8080/api/genres/movie/1

### Add a genre to a movie (Success)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/genres/movie/1/2

### Remove a genre from a movie (Success)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/genres/movie/1/2

### Remove a genre from a movie (Failure - genre not found)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/genres/movie/1/999
